{"title":"歌谣四则","authors":["村野"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":6,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌谣四则"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边哭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海官僚通宵舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖南灾民同跳河；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同在大中华民国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边欢乐一边哭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好招牌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仓库麦子回了芽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百姓饿死在四野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民生两字好招牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗腿权作羊肉卖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君子一言就算定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小人文书不作证；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明里开放暗里禁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诺言两字不分明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独家享"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天这里打一场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天那里搜查忙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别家报馆打个光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"言论自由独家享。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（录自四月廿一日时代日报星空）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}